commit.message: Way of calling blas changed in Makefile, but forgot to update README
update version number of setup.py because of mistakes in testing PyPI.
update version number and COPYRIGHT file for 2.46

Set pointers to NULL after memory is freed

Signed-off-by: Sinacam <stinkingmadgod@gmail.com>

Some improvements/changes in the one-class SVM solver:

- use quickselect and quicksort instead of heap to shorten the running
   time on finding violating pairs. See details in a new section in
   supplementary materials of our linear one-class SVM paper.

- modify the comparison function so instances with the same gradient
   values are ordered by their instance indices. This ensures the same
   results by using different implementations (e.g.,
   quickselect/quicksort vs. heap)
Update README: For nr_class = 1 or 2, solvers except MCSVM_CS return a single vector of weight.
added MacOS wheel to github actions
changed version detection to use make conditional statement
